data.description: Adorable 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home for sale in Pahrump, Nevada! Centrally located on a quiet road, just steps away from walking paths and a short drive to schools, shopping, and medical services. This well-maintained home boasts a very spacious split floorplan, with a large kitchen and pantry, solar covers on windows and ceiling fans throughout! The fully fenced backyard has a storage shed and easy maintenance landscaping. Comstock Park Community features a community pool, recreation center and a separate parking area for your RV or trailer. Don't miss out on this one!
